  <data name="Assist.Q.MyTasks" xml:space="preserve"><value>Where can I see my tasks?</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.A.MyTasks" xml:space="preserve"><value>You can find all tasks assigned to you on the &lt;strong&gt;📋 My Tasks&lt;/strong&gt; page in the left menu.</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.L.MyTasks" xml:space="preserve"><value>Go to my tasks</value></data>

  <data name="Assist.Q.NewTask" xml:space="preserve"><value>How do I create a new task?</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.A.NewTask" xml:space="preserve"><value>To create a new task, go to the &lt;strong&gt;➕ New Task&lt;/strong&gt; page in the left menu. You can only assign tasks to people on your team.</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.L.NewTask" xml:space="preserve"><value>Create new task</value></data>

  <data name="Assist.Q.AssignedByMe" xml:space="preserve"><value>How do I track the tasks I've assigned?</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.A.AssignedByMe" xml:space="preserve"><value>You can see the tasks you've assigned on the &lt;strong&gt;📝 Tasks I Assigned&lt;/strong&gt; page.</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.L.AssignedByMe" xml:space="preserve"><value>View tasks I assigned</value></data>

  <data name="Assist.Q.Password" xml:space="preserve"><value>How do I change my password?</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.A.Password" xml:space="preserve"><value>&lt;strong&gt;Account → My Profile → Change My Password&lt;/strong&gt;. You need to enter your current password and the new one.</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.L.Password" xml:space="preserve"><value>Change password</value></data>

  <data name="Assist.Q.Profile" xml:space="preserve"><value>How do I update my profile?</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.A.Profile" xml:space="preserve"><value>You can update info like your phone number and accounting code from your profile. &lt;strong&gt;Account → My Profile&lt;/strong&gt;.</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.L.Profile" xml:space="preserve"><value>Go to my profile</value></data>

  <data name="Assist.Q.NewUser" xml:space="preserve"><value>How do I add a new user?</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.A.NewUser" xml:space="preserve"><value>&lt;strong&gt;Management → Users → ➕ New User&lt;/strong&gt;. The manager field is important for the hierarchy.</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.L.NewUser" xml:space="preserve"><value>Add new user</value></data>

  <data name="Assist.Q.Roles" xml:space="preserve"><value>How are roles and authorities assigned?</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.A.Roles" xml:space="preserve"><value>&lt;strong&gt;Management → Roles and Authorities&lt;/strong&gt;. Use the ⚡ Authorities button next to a role to assign authorities.</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.L.Roles" xml:space="preserve"><value>Go to roles</value></data>

  <data name="Assist.Q.Departments" xml:space="preserve"><value>How do I add a department?</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.A.Departments" xml:space="preserve"><value>You can add it from &lt;strong&gt;Management → Departments → ➕ New Department&lt;/strong&gt;.</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.L.Departments" xml:space="preserve"><value>Add new department</value></data>

  <data name="Assist.Q.OrgChart" xml:space="preserve"><value>How do I view the organization chart?</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.A.OrgChart" xml:space="preserve"><value>You can view it as a tree from &lt;strong&gt;General → Organization Chart&lt;/strong&gt;.</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.L.OrgChart" xml:space="preserve"><value>View chart</value></data>

  <data name="Assist.Q.Gmail" xml:space="preserve"><value>How do I open Gmail?</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.A.Gmail" xml:space="preserve"><value>Click the red &lt;strong&gt;📩 Open Gmail&lt;/strong&gt; button in the top right of the home page to open your Gmail account in a new tab.</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.L.Gmail" xml:space="preserve"><value>Open Gmail now</value></data>

  <data name="Assist.Q.Propose" xml:space="preserve"><value>How do I report work?</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.A.Propose" xml:space="preserve"><value>If there's work that needs to be done, you can report it to your manager from the &lt;strong&gt;📩 Report Work&lt;/strong&gt; page. Once approved, it will be added to your active tasks.</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.L.Propose" xml:space="preserve"><value>Report work</value></data>

  <data name="Assist.Q.Pending" xml:space="preserve"><value>How do I view pending approval items?</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.A.Pending" xml:space="preserve"><value>You can view work reports from your team on the &lt;strong&gt;⏳ Pending Approvals&lt;/strong&gt; page. You can approve each one or reject with a reason.</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.L.Pending" xml:space="preserve"><value>View pending approvals</value></data>

  <data name="Assist.Q.Logout" xml:space="preserve"><value>How do I log out?</value></data>
  <data name="Assist.A.Logout" xml:space="preserve"><value>Click the &lt;strong&gt;🚪 Logout&lt;/strong&gt; button in the top right to log out securely.</value></data>
